<p>Not what you're looking for? <%= mail_to("hello@openlectures.org", "Let's talk!", :encode => "javascript") %>. We'll work things out for you.</p>
<h3 class="marginbot0">Paradise</h3>
<p>Every weekend at openlectures is full of surprises. It's a large happy family who'll willingly try a thousand things to get one lecture done right. <span class="salmon">When you join us, you join our family.</span></p>
<div class="row-fluid">
<div class="span4">
  <div class="align-center margintop-h3 marginbot-h3">
    <%=image_tag 'work.png'%>
  </div><!--aligncenter-->
<p><span class="olgreen">We've got issues with locking people in a room.</span> Work from home, at Starbucks, or in our comfortable bean-bag caves. Some people even roost on the ole' Porcelain Throne for the inspiration it provides.</p>
</div><!--span4-->
<div class="span4">
  <div class="align-center margintop-h3 marginbot-h3">
    <%=image_tag 'levitation.png'%>
  </div><!--aligncenter-->
<p><span class="olgreen">We respect your judgment.</span> Need a break? It's yours. If it takes you a trip to Paris to get things done, we'll wait. For senior employees, we even dispatch a minion to the airport to do the hand-waving up close and personal.</p>
</div><!--span4-->
<div class="span4">
  <div class="align-center margintop-h3 marginbot-h3">
